---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro'
import ArchitectureDiagram from '../../components/ArchitectureDiagram.astro'
---

<Layout
  titulo="GitOps Platform Architecture | LRA Cloud Operations"
  descripcion="Automated delivery pipeline with Git as the single source of truth. GitHub Actions for CI, ArgoCD for CD, OIDC authentication throughout the entire pipeline."
  keywords="GitOps architecture ArgoCD, GitHub Actions CI/CD pipeline, GitOps delivery pipeline, ArgoCD Kubernetes deployment, OIDC CI/CD"
>

  <section class="relative overflow-hidden" style="background-color: #0A2540;">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none" style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(147,184,255,0.15) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 28px 28px;"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 sm:py-20">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs mb-8" style="color: rgba(147,184,255,0.5);">
        <a href="/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors" style="color: rgba(147,184,255,0.5);">Home</a>
        <span>/</span>
        <a href="/architectures" class="hover:text-white transition-colors" style="color: rgba(147,184,255,0.5);">Architectures</a>
        <span>/</span>
        <span style="color: rgba(147,184,255,0.9);">GitOps Platform</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-5">
        <span class="text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full" style="background: #f0fdf4; color: #15803d; border: 1px solid #bbf7d0;">Production Tested</span>
        <span class="text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full" style="background: rgba(255,108,55,0.15); color: #FF6C37; border: 1px solid rgba(255,108,55,0.3);">GitOps</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white mb-4" style="letter-spacing: -0.02em;">GitOps Platform</h1>
      <p class="text-lg max-w-2xl" style="color: rgba(147,184,255,0.8);">Automated delivery with Git as the single source of truth. Every deployment is tracked, versioned and automatically rolled back if something fails.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
        <div class="lg:col-span-2 space-y-10">

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #0A2540;">Overview</h2>
            <p class="text-base leading-relaxed mb-4" style="color: #64748b;">This platform separates CI (build, test, push) from CD (deploy, verify). GitHub Actions owns the CI pipeline and produces a container image tagged with the commit SHA. ArgoCD owns the CD pipeline and applies whatever the Git configuration repository declares as the desired state.</p>
            <p class="text-base leading-relaxed" style="color: #64748b;">No human or machine has direct kubectl access to production. Every change must go through a pull request to the configuration repository. ArgoCD detects the change and applies it. If the new pods fail health checks, ArgoCD stops and reverts. Every deployment is auditable — the Git commit history is the deployment history.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #0A2540;">Architecture Diagram</h2>
            <ArchitectureDiagram title="GitOps Platform — CI/CD Flow" description="Separation of CI (build) and CD (deploy) with Git as the source of truth for both." archId="gitops-platform">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 720 340" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-full" style="min-width: 520px; font-family: Inter, system-ui, sans-serif;">

                <!-- Developer -->
                <rect x="10" y="130" width="80" height="50" rx="8" fill="#F8FAFC" stroke="#e2e8f0" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                <text x="50" y="150" text-anchor="middle" fill="#0A2540" font-size="10" font-weight="700">Developer</text>
                <text x="50" y="165" text-anchor="middle" fill="#64748b" font-size="8">git push</text>
                <text x="50" y="175" text-anchor="middle" fill="#64748b" font-size="8">feature/...</text>

                <!-- Arrow to App Repo -->
                <line x1="90" y1="155" x2="120" y2="155" stroke="#1E6FFF" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#a1)"/>

                <!-- App Repo -->
                <rect x="120" y="130" width="90" height="50" rx="8" fill="#EEF4FF" stroke="#1E6FFF" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                <text x="165" y="150" text-anchor="middle" fill="#0A2540" font-size="10" font-weight="700">App Repo</text>
                <text x="165" y="163" text-anchor="middle" fill="#64748b" font-size="8">source code</text>
                <text x="165" y="174" text-anchor="middle" fill="#64748b" font-size="8">GitHub PR → merge</text>

                <!-- Arrow to CI -->
                <line x1="210" y1="155" x2="240" y2="155" stroke="#1E6FFF" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#a1)"/>

                <!-- GitHub Actions CI box -->
                <rect x="240" y="90" width="130" height="140" rx="8" fill="#F8FAFC" stroke="#333" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                <text x="305" y="112" text-anchor="middle" fill="#0A2540" font-size="10" font-weight="700">GitHub Actions CI</text>
                <text x="305" y="130" text-anchor="middle" fill="#64748b" font-size="8">① Lint + Unit Tests</text>
                <text x="305" y="145" text-anchor="middle" fill="#64748b" font-size="8">② SAST (SonarQube)</text>
                <text x="305" y="160" text-anchor="middle" fill="#64748b" font-size="8">③ Docker Build</text>
                <text x="305" y="175" text-anchor="middle" fill="#64748b" font-size="8">④ ECR Push (:sha)</text>
                <text x="305" y="190" text-anchor="middle" fill="#059669" font-size="8" font-weight="600">⑤ Update config repo</text>
                <text x="305" y="205" text-anchor="middle" fill="#64748b" font-size="8">image.tag → commit sha</text>
                <text x="305" y="218" text-anchor="middle" fill="#94A3B8" font-size="7">OIDC — no static keys</text>

                <!-- Arrow to Config Repo -->
                <line x1="370" y1="155" x2="400" y2="155" stroke="#059669" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="4,3" marker-end="url(#a2)"/>

                <!-- Config Repo -->
                <rect x="400" y="130" width="100" height="50" rx="8" fill="#F0FDF4" stroke="#059669" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                <text x="450" y="150" text-anchor="middle" fill="#0A2540" font-size="10" font-weight="700">Config Repo</text>
                <text x="450" y="163" text-anchor="middle" fill="#64748b" font-size="8">Helm values</text>
                <text x="450" y="174" text-anchor="middle" fill="#64748b" font-size="8">ArgoCD Applications</text>

                <!-- Arrow to ArgoCD -->
                <line x1="500" y1="155" x2="530" y2="155" stroke="#FF6C37" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#a3)"/>

                <!-- ArgoCD box -->
                <rect x="530" y="100" width="120" height="110" rx="8" fill="#FFF5F0" stroke="#FF6C37" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                <text x="590" y="122" text-anchor="middle" fill="#0A2540" font-size="10" font-weight="700">ArgoCD</text>
                <text x="590" y="140" text-anchor="middle" fill="#64748b" font-size="8">Watch config repo</text>
                <text x="590" y="155" text-anchor="middle" fill="#64748b" font-size="8">Detect drift</text>
                <text x="590" y="170" text-anchor="middle" fill="#64748b" font-size="8">Apply to EKS</text>
                <text x="590" y="185" text-anchor="middle" fill="#64748b" font-size="8">Health check</text>
                <text x="590" y="200" text-anchor="middle" fill="#DC2626" font-size="8">Rollback on failure</text>

                <!-- Arrow to EKS -->
                <line x1="590" y1="210" x2="590" y2="240" stroke="#FF6C37" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#a3)"/>
                <rect x="530" y="240" width="120" height="40" rx="8" fill="#326CE5" fill-opacity="0.12" stroke="#326CE5" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                <text x="590" y="257" text-anchor="middle" fill="#0A2540" font-size="10" font-weight="700">EKS Cluster</text>
                <text x="590" y="270" text-anchor="middle" fill="#64748b" font-size="8">Rolling update · HPA</text>

                <!-- Rollback arrow -->
                <path d="M 650 250 C 680 250 680 155 650 155" stroke="#DC2626" stroke-width="1" fill="none" stroke-dasharray="3,3" marker-end="url(#a4)"/>
                <text x="685" y="205" fill="#DC2626" font-size="8" transform="rotate(90,685,205)">auto rollback</text>

                <!-- ECR -->
                <rect x="370" y="20" width="90" height="35" rx="6" fill="#F8FAFC" stroke="#e2e8f0" stroke-width="1"/>
                <text x="415" y="35" text-anchor="middle" fill="#0A2540" font-size="9" font-weight="600">ECR</text>
                <text x="415" y="47" text-anchor="middle" fill="#64748b" font-size="8">Container images</text>
                <line x1="305" y1="90" x2="415" y2="55" stroke="#e2e8f0" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="3,3" marker-end="url(#a5)"/>
                <line x1="415" y1="55" x2="590" y2="100" stroke="#e2e8f0" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="3,3" marker-end="url(#a5)"/>

                <defs>
                  <marker id="a1" markerWidth="6" markerHeight="6" refX="5" refY="3" orient="auto"><path d="M0,0 L0,6 L6,3 z" fill="#1E6FFF"/></marker>
                  <marker id="a2" markerWidth="6" markerHeight="6" refX="5" refY="3" orient="auto"><path d="M0,0 L0,6 L6,3 z" fill="#059669"/></marker>
                  <marker id="a3" markerWidth="6" markerHeight="6" refX="5" refY="3" orient="auto"><path d="M0,0 L0,6 L6,3 z" fill="#FF6C37"/></marker>
                  <marker id="a4" markerWidth="6" markerHeight="6" refX="5" refY="3" orient="auto"><path d="M0,0 L0,6 L6,3 z" fill="#DC2626"/></marker>
                  <marker id="a5" markerWidth="6" markerHeight="6" refX="5" refY="3" orient="auto"><path d="M0,0 L0,6 L6,3 z" fill="#CBD5E1"/></marker>
                </defs>
              </svg>
            </ArchitectureDiagram>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-5" style="color: #0A2540;">Pipeline Stages</h2>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              {[
                { stage: 'CI — Code quality', detail: 'Lint, unit tests, SAST scan with SonarQube. Coverage gate ≥80%. If any stage fails, the pipeline stops. No image is built from code that fails quality gates.', color: '#1E6FFF' },
                { stage: 'CI — Build and push', detail: 'Multi-stage Dockerfile. Non-root user. Image tagged with full commit SHA — never "latest" in production. Pushed to ECR private registry.', color: '#326CE5' },
                { stage: 'CI — Update config repo', detail: 'Automated PR to config repo updating image.tag in Helm values. Triggers ArgoCD sync detection. Uses OIDC token — no Git credentials stored in CI.', color: '#059669' },
                { stage: 'CD — ArgoCD sync', detail: 'ArgoCD detects config repo change. Compares desired state (Git) with actual state (EKS). Applies Helm release with rolling update strategy.', color: '#FF6C37' },
                { stage: 'CD — Health verification', detail: 'ArgoCD monitors pod health probes during rollout. If readiness probe fails, deployment is halted and reverted to previous revision automatically.', color: '#D97706' },
              ].map(({ stage, detail, color }) => (
                <div class="flex gap-4 p-5 rounded-xl" style="background: #F8FAFC; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;">
                  <div class="w-2 rounded-full flex-shrink-0 mt-1" style={`background: ${color};`}></div>
                  <div>
                    <h3 class="text-sm font-bold mb-1" style="color: #0A2540;">{stage}</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: #64748b;">{detail}</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              ))}
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>

        <div class="lg:col-span-1">
          <div class="sticky top-24 space-y-5">
            <div class="rounded-2xl p-6" style="background: #F8FAFC; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;">
              <h3 class="text-sm font-bold mb-4" style="color: #0A2540;">Stack</h3>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
                {['ArgoCD', 'Helm', 'GitHub Actions', 'OIDC', 'ECR', 'EKS', 'SonarQube', 'Docker'].map(tag => (
                  <span class="text-xs px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full" style="background: white; color: #64748b; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;">{tag}</span>
                ))}
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-2xl p-6" style="background: #EEF4FF; border: 1px solid #c3d9ff;">
              <h3 class="text-sm font-bold mb-2" style="color: #0A2540;">Need this implemented?</h3>
              <p class="text-xs leading-relaxed mb-4" style="color: #64748b;">We implement complete GitOps platforms from pipeline to cluster. Turnkey delivery in 3–4 weeks.</p>
              <a href="/contact" class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-sm font-bold text-white py-3 rounded-xl hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity" style="background: #1E6FFF;">Start a conversation →</a>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-2xl p-5" style="background: white; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;">
              <h3 class="text-xs font-bold mb-3 uppercase tracking-wider" style="color: #94A3B8;">Related</h3>
              <div class="space-y-2">
                <a href="/docs/gitops-standards" class="block text-sm font-medium hover:opacity-70 transition-opacity" style="color: #1E6FFF;">GitOps Standards Guide →</a>
                <a href="/projects/gitops-stack" class="block text-sm font-medium hover:opacity-70 transition-opacity" style="color: #1E6FFF;">GitOps Stack case study →</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<script>
  if (typeof window !== 'undefined' && (window as any).cf) {
    (window as any).cf.track('architecture_viewed', { architecture: 'gitops-platform' })
  }
</script>
